# sudoers_file_modification
#
# This Analytic predicate may be used to report on all modifications made to the /etc/sudoers file on an endpoint.
# This detection functions by monitoring for modifications made to the /etc/sudoers file path.
#
# Analytic Predicate(s):

$event.path == "/etc/sudoers" AND $event.isModified == 1

# Required Analytic Configuration:

Sensor Event Type: File System Event

# Recommended Analytic Configuration:

Severity: Informational
Level: 0
